import React from "react"
import { Container, Row, Col } from "reactstrap"
import {
  fastFoodProducts,
  riceMenuProducts,
  pizzaProducts,
  dessertProducts,
  coffeeProducts
} from "../../assets/fake-data/products"

const MenuPack = () => {
  return (
    <section>
      <Container>
        <Row>
          <Col lg='12' className='text-center mb-5'></Col>
          <Col lg='12' className='text-center mb-4'>
            <button className="btn">Fast Food</button>
            <button className="btn">Rice Menu</button>
            <button className="btn">Pizza</button>
            <button className="btn">Desserts</button>
            <button className="btn">Coffee</button>
          </Col>

          {fastFoodProducts.map(item=>(
            <Col lg="3" key={item.id}></Col>
          ))}
        </Row>
      </Container>
    </section>
  )
}

export default MenuPack
